@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Maverick";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>In this page we show a AI chatbox that determines your behavior style based on a dialoque with you! Take the maverick decision to be honest. <br />Be a maverick person to investigate with an open mind the AI's reflections.</p>

<div class="maverick-ai-chatbox">
    <div class="maverick-image-container"></div>
    <div class="maverick-chat-message">
        User: Show me the image of the maverick hero.
    </div>
    <div class="maverick-chat-message maverick-ai-response">
        <div class="maverick-chat-message">AI: Here is the image of the maverick hero.</div>
    </div>
</div>

<h1>Behavioral Style</h1>
<h2>Best category</h2>
Green is category best described determined and points distributed
<div class="maverick-container" id="maverick-best"></div>
<h2>Worst category</h2>
Red is category worst described determined and points distributed
<div class="maverick-container" id="maverick-worst"></div>

<script src="~/js/maverick.js" asp-append-version="true"></script>
